UNITED STATES of America v. Luis M. SANCHEZ et al. No. 2309. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. May 9, 1941. Everett M. Grantham, U. S. Atty., of Santa Fe, N. M., for appellant. R. F. Deacon Arledge, of Albuquerque, N. M., for appellees.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed May 6, 1941, on motion of appellant.
